title: #122: Popping Minds With Freeman Fly
description: Thank you for tuning in for another interesting episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  This episode I welcome one of originators of the interest truth movement, Freeman Fly.  Freeman discusses how he got into the world of conspiracies, the history of the Freemans and his theory of on Obama and let's just say A-Aron wasn't buying any of it.  All of this and more on a very exciting new episode.
